  "contentHtml": "\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <p><img src=\"https://health.economictimes.indiatimes.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/et-default-user.svg\" alt=\"Shilpa Ranipeta\">\n                                            \n                                        </p>\n                                                                        \n                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                                    <li>\n                                                                                                                                                                            <a>Shilpa Ranipeta</a>\n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                                                                                                            </li>\n                                                                                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/agency/88675387/ET-Bureau\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ET Bureau</a></li>\n                                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                                <ul>\n                                                                                            <li>Published On Jun 16, 2026 at 07:20 AM IST</li>\n                                                                                                                                </ul>\n                                    \n                                                                            \n                                                                        \n                                \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure><p>Hyderabad: Medical technology and scientific publishing company <a href=\"/tag/pulsus+group\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Pulsus Group</a> has announced that it will invest Rs 500 crore to expand its <a href=\"/tag/ai+healthcare\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">AI healthcare</a> and digital innovation hub at Ameenpur in Telangana, targeting the creation of 6,000 direct jobs and an estimated 30,000 indirect jobs as it scales operations at the 35-acre campus.The expansion follows a recent Supreme Court ruling that upheld the project's IT/ITeS Park and Special Economic Zone (SEZ) status, clearing the way for accelerated development and fresh investments at the site near Miyapur.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>The company said the legal clarity provided by the ruling would enable it to fast-track plans to develop the campus into a major hub for artificial intelligence, healthcare technology and digital services.</p>\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        <p>\"The Ameenpur project, located near Miyapur, was envisioned as a hub for technology and employment generation. Despite delays caused by legal and regulatory challenges, we remained committed to this vision,\" said Dr. Gedela Srinubabu, CEO of Pulsus Group.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>According to Pulsus, the expanded campus will focus on artificial intelligence-led healthcare solutions, digital services, clinical research support and healthcare data analytics. The company also plans to collaborate with universities, research institutions, healthcare organisations, startups and technology firms to support innovation and talent development.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>The company said the project is expected to create demand for software engineers, AI specialists, healthcare data scientists, bioinformatics experts, clinical research associates and other digital services professionals, further strengthening Telangana's growing technology and life sciences ecosystem.                    </p><!-- Category Most Read Placement -->\n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                                                            <!-- <li>By <span>Shilpa Ranipeta</span>,</li> -->\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <li>By\n                                                                                            <a>Shilpa Ranipeta</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                        , \n                                                                                    </li>\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/88675387/ET-Bureau\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ET Bureau</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On Jun 16, 2026 at 07:20 AM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On Jun 16, 2026 at 07:20 AM IST</li>\n                    